00:32:10.880 --> 00:32:12.880
the power of your word.

00:32:12.880 --> 00:32:15.880
I thank you for the impact that this reality had

00:32:15.880 --> 00:32:19.880
in the life of David, the life of Joshua, Jeremiah,

00:32:19.880 --> 00:32:21.880
the disciples.

00:32:21.880 --> 00:32:23.880
God, this evening, as much as we can rejoice

00:32:23.880 --> 00:32:28.880
in reading the accounts and recognizing the impact

00:32:28.880 --> 00:32:31.880
of this truth in the lives of these individuals,

00:32:31.880 --> 00:32:34.880
I pray tonight that you would help us

00:32:34.880 --> 00:32:38.880
to have our lives, our behavior impacted

00:32:38.880 --> 00:32:40.880
by this truth, this promise.

00:32:40.880 --> 00:32:42.880
Thou art with me.

00:32:42.880 --> 00:32:46.880
Help us to live each day with the awareness

00:32:46.880 --> 00:32:48.880
that my shepherd's with me.

00:32:48.880 --> 00:32:51.880
I pray they have a great impact on our lives.

00:32:51.880 --> 00:32:53.880
I pray that you'd bless the time of prayer.

00:32:53.880 --> 00:32:54.880
We thank you for the privilege.

00:32:54.880 --> 00:32:56.880
We thank you for the opportunity.

00:32:56.880 --> 00:32:58.880
We thank you that you're a God who hears and answers.

00:32:58.880 --> 00:33:01.880
We pray, God, that you would have your will in way

00:33:01.880 --> 00:33:04.880
through the remainder of this service tonight.

00:33:04.880 --> 00:33:07.880
For it's in Christ's name we pray, amen.

